===Noun===
'''Kirchoff's circuit laws'''
#{{physics}} a pair of [[fundamental]] [[natural]] [[law]]s dealing with the [[relation]]s of [[current]]s at a [[junction]] and the [[voltage]]s around a [[loop]]
